title: Holy Land Middle Eastern Market
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Traditional Middle Eastern cuisine with veg choices including hummus (original, black olive and scallion, roasted red pepper, roasted garlic), tabouli salad, baba ghanouj, mujadara, kushari, and such. Will accommodate vegans. Frequented by the Knoxville vegan meet-up group. A small grocery store and a fresh olive bar are also on premises.
